  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nIt's possible to have two cross-origin parents with insufficient framing protections use the same session history entry when navigating history by using location.replace(). By creating a history entry in a subframe, then replacing the parent frame's active history entry"
